
# Serverless Cloud Dictionary App

A serverless cloud-based dictionary application built using AWS services and React.js.

---

# AWS Services Used

- AWS Lambda
- API Gateway
- DynamoDB
- React.js
- Python (Boto3)

---

# Architecture

Frontend → API Gateway → Lambda → DynamoDB

